(465, 1, 6, 1, 25, '01025', 'The Winds of Winter', NULL, NULL, '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-13 10:10:52', 1, 3, 2, 4, 5, 2, NULL, 'Winter.', 'A cold wind was blowing out of the north, and it made the trees rustle like living things. All day, Will had felt as though something were watching him, something cold and implacable that loved him not.', 'Tomasz Jedruszek', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '05c62b13-053b-4b81-a0a8-bf1d3f19210f'),
(466, 1, 6, 1, 26, '01026', 'Wildfire Assault', NULL, '<b>When Revealed:</b> Each player chooses up to 3 characters he or she controls. Kill each character not chosen (cannot be saved).', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-13 10:10:52', 2, 4, 1, 7, 6, 2, NULL, 'Scheme. War.', NULL, 'Tomasz Jedruszek', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'd10a1ced-df94-419b-af8e-4eadc2eb4688'),
(467, 1, 1, 1, 27, '01027', 'Fealty', NULL, 'You cannot include more than 15 neutral cards in your deck.\n<b>Action:</b> Kneel your faction card to reduce the cost of the next loyal card you marshal or play this phase by 1.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Magali Villeneuve', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '83754e87-8448-49af-a20f-bc4dc72d1dba'),
(468, 1, 3, 1, 28, '01028', 'Littlefinger', 5, '<b>Reaction:</b> After you marshal Littlefinger, draw 2 cards.\n+1 Income.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Ally. Lord. Small Council.', '"I did warn you not to trust me."', 'Christopher Bradley', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, '499ed82d-cc0e-43a5-89ba-a748b388f528'),
(469, 1, 3, 1, 29, '01029', 'Varys', 6, '<abbr>Stealth</abbr>.\n<b>Interrupt:</b> When the dominance phase ends, remove Varys from the game to discard each character from play.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 3, 'Lord. Small Council. Spy.', '"Why is it always the innocents who suffer most, when you high lords play your game of thrones?"', 'Mike Capprotti', 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, '78845c6e-c91a-47a2-9742-d72b19d0ed26'),
(470, 1, 2, 1, 34, '01034', 'Little Bird', 1, 'Attached character gains an [intrigue] icon.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Condition.', '"He has informants everywhere. His little birds, he calls them." <cite>Littlefinger</cite>', 'Melissa Findley', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'b30f1522-c57b-493a-ad11-1088c05046ea'),
(471, 1, 2, 1, 35, '01035', 'Milk of the Poppy', 1, '<abbr>Terminal</abbr>.\nTreat attached character''s printed text box as if it were blank (except for <i>Traits</i>).', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Condition.', 'By the time the maester removed the funnel from his mouth, he was already spiralling back to sleep.', 'Kara Williams', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'a8bebc54-d01c-424d-8839-460ec09b733f'),
(472, 1, 2, 1, 37, '01037', 'Syrio''s Training', 1, 'Attached character gains a [military] icon.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Condition. Skill.', '"Now we will begin the dance." <cite>Syrio Forel</cite>', 'Ryan Barger', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'aec7e23f-3e46-49b9-bd6b-37075b3646dd'),
(473, 1, 5, 1, 38, '01038', 'The Iron Throne', 2, 'The Iron Throne contributes 8 STR to your total for dominance.\n+1 Reserve.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'King''s Landing.', '"…it is a monstruous uncomfortable chair. In more ways than one." <cite>Robert Baratheon</cite>', 'Jacob Murray', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '32b0d392-802e-4b0b-9df5-dd0eeee256b9'),
(474, 1, 5, 1, 39, '01039', 'The Kingsroad', 1, '<abbr>Limited</abbr>.\n<b>Marshaling Action:</b> Kneel and sacrifice The Kingsroad to reduce the cost of the next character you marshal this phase by 3.\n+1 Initiative.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Westeros.', NULL, 'Julepe', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '90452d99-6a6f-4d0d-b3a1-bb92e7110d1d'),
(475, 1, 5, 1, 40, '01040', 'The Roseroad', 0, '<abbr>Limited</abbr>.\n+1 Income.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Westeros.', NULL, 'Ted Nasmith', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '51a3e04f-3f44-4417-8d7c-1f116acd5c80'),
(476, 1, 4, 1, 43, '01043', 'Superior Claim', 0, '<b>Reaction:</b> After you win a [power] challenge by 5 or more STR, gain 2 power for your faction. (Max 1 per challenge.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jason Engle', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '8e9b06da-991e-4608-a16b-caf96209641a'),
(477, 1, 3, 2, 46, '01046', 'Maester Cressen', 3, '<b>Marshalling Action:</b> Kneel Maester Cressen to choose a <i>Condition</i> attachment, and discard it from play.', '2015-07-09 10:43:53', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 3, 'Maester.', NULL, 'J. Edwin Stevens', 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0c97b091-96c0-46df-8442-e904025304fb'),
(478, 1, 3, 2, 47, '01047', 'Melisandre', 5, '<b>Reaction:</b> After you marshal or play a <i>R''hllor</i> card, choose and kneel a character. (Limit once per round.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Lady. R''hllor.', '"It is not the foes who curse you to your face that you must fear, but those who smile when you are looking and sharpen their knives when you turn your back."', 'Jacob Murray', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, '6ab37ed8-df99-410d-a9ff-7afe98f7ee22'),
(479, 1, 3, 2, 48, '01048', 'Robert Baratheon', 7, '<abbr>Intimidate</abbr>. <abbr>Renown</abbr>.\nRobert Baratheon gets +1 STR for each other kneeling character in play.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 5, 'King. Lord.', '"Fat? Fat, is it? Is that how your speak to your king? Ah, damn you, Ned, why are you always right?"', 'Joshua Cairós', 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, '78ca6089-6d16-4e41-8df7-40042e3dc077'),
(480, 1, 3, 2, 49, '01049', 'Selyse Baratheon', 3, '<b>Challenges Action:</b> Pay 1 gold to choose a [baratheon] character. Until the end of the phase, that character gains an [intrigue] icon.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, 'House Florent. Lady. R''hllor.', NULL, 'Tawny Fritzinger', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, '88de8a8f-4d15-415c-96c8-38edc8f8fe99'),
(481, 1, 3, 2, 52, '01052', 'Stannis Baratheon', 6, 'Each player cannot stand more than 2 characters during the standing phase.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 5, 'Lord. Small Council.', '"I shall bring justice to Westeros."', 'Joshua Cairós', 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 'dfc85d0c-12a5-45b3-803a-98982c36d083'),
(482, 1, 3, 2, 54, '01054', 'Fiery Followers', 3, '<b>Reaction:</b> After the dominance phase begins, stand Fiery Followers.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, 'R''hllor.', '"The red priests have a great temple on Lys. Always they are burning this and burning that, crying out to their R''hllor. They bore me with their fires. Soon they will bore King Stannis too, it is to be hoped." <cite>Salladhor Saan</cite>', 'Jarreau Wimberly', 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, '21c87233-3c2e-4a66-9ea0-ffaf5ac0594c'),
(483, 1, 2, 2, 58, '01058', 'Lightbringer', 2, '[baratheon] character only.\nIf attached character is Stannis Baratheon, he gains <abbr>renown</abbr>.\n<b>Reaction:</b> After attached character gains 1 or more power, stand it. (Limit once per phase.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'R''hllor. Weapon.', NULL, 'John Matson', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '7e00c4df-c406-4560-9cb1-a18b1a180017'),
(484, 1, 5, 2, 60, '01060', 'Chamber of the Painted Table', 2, '<b>Reaction:</b> After you win dominance, kneel Chamber of the Painted Table to move 1 power from an opponent''s faction card to your own.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Dragonstone.', NULL, 'Mariusz Gandzel', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '8b8d9c4c-a100-4d95-b68b-5156766035d9'),
(485, 1, 5, 2, 61, '01061', 'The Red Keep', 3, 'The Red Keep contributes 2 STR to your side during any [power] challenge in which you control a participating character.\n<b>Interrupt:</b> When the challenges phase ends, if you have not lost a [power] challenge this round, kneel The Red Keep to draw 2 cards.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'King''s Landing.', NULL, 'Tomasz Jedruszek', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '3a89059b-0e56-4b47-aad7-8d2b0a245149'),
(486, 1, 4, 2, 62, '01062', 'Consolidation of Power', 1, '<b>Marshaling Action:</b> Choose and kneel up to 4 total STR worth of characters controlled by the same player. Then, choose one of those characters, and have it gain 1 power.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Regis Moulun', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'b1092dd9-01aa-4622-9026-d905a44dd874'),
(487, 1, 4, 2, 63, '01063', 'Ours is the Fury', 2, 'Play only during a challenge in which you are the defending player.\n<b>Action:</b> Choose a kneeling [baratheon] character you control. That character is now participating as a defender. If you win this challenge, stand that character.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Joshua Cairós', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '9d1702a8-32c9-41c2-bbd4-2ce00885e20a'),
(488, 1, 4, 2, 64, '01064', 'Seen In Flames', 1, 'Play only if you control a <i>R''hllor</i> character.\n<b>Challenges Action:</b> Choose an opponent, and look at his or her hand. Then, choose and discard 1 card from that hand.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'R''hllor.', NULL, 'Nacho Molina', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '50402306-cc27-4e3e-9924-aa13f430cb60'),
(489, 1, 3, 3, 65, '01065', 'Aeron Damphair', 3, '<b>Reaction:</b> After you win dominance, put an <i>Ironborn</i> character into play from your dead pile.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 3, 'Drowned God. Ironborn. Lord.', '"What is dead may never die, but rises again, harder and stronger."', 'Anders Finer', 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'c4fbe19b-fe3b-4f5c-b1c6-065c13c4a9db'),
(490, 1, 3, 3, 67, '01067', 'Asha Greyjoy', 5, '<abbr>Stealth</abbr>.\n<b>Reaction:</b> After you win an unopposed challenge in which Asha Greyjoy is participating, stand her.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Ironborn. Lady.', '"I am Asha of House Greyjoy, aye. Opinions differ on whether I''m a lady."', 'Mark Behm', 1, 0, 1, 0, 1, '41367a9d-b751-4632-9973-97d2e4df7087'),
(491, 1, 3, 3, 68, '01068', 'Balon Greyjoy', 6, '<abbr>Renown</abbr>.\nWhile Balon Greyjoy is attacking, each defending character with a lower STR than his does not contribute its STR to that challenge.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 5, 'Ironborn. Lord.', '"I am the Greyjoy, Lord Reaper of Pyke, King of Salt and Rock, Son of the Sea Wind, and no man gives me a crown. I pay the iron price."', 'Sebastian Ciaffaglione', 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, '9bc99c98-4cbd-467b-b31c-1bec686370ea'),
(492, 1, 3, 3, 69, '01069', 'Euron Crow''s Eye', 7, '<abbr>Pillage</abbr>. <abbr>Renown</abbr>.\n<b>Reaction:</b> After Euron Crow''s Eye discards a card using <abbr>pillage</abbr>, put a location from the losing opponent''s discard pile into play under your control.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 6, 'Ironborn. Lord. Raider.', '"The Crow''s Eye worships naught but his own pride." <cite>Aeron Damphair</cite>', 'J.B. Casacop', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '912e5447-89b3-4896-903c-6f5ed78113e1'),
(493, 1, 3, 3, 70, '01070', 'Maester Wendamyr', 2, '<abbr>Stealth</abbr>.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, 'Maester.', 'He wore about his neck a chain of many metals that marked him for a master of the Citadel.', 'Aleksander Karcz', 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, '1913dcf2-dc68-4427-a3ae-5deb5e054d8c'),
(494, 1, 3, 3, 74, '01074', 'Iron Islands Fishmonger', 1, '<b>Marshaling Action:</b> Kneel Iron Islands Fishmonger to reduce the cost of the next [greyjoy] character you marshal this phase by 1.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 1, 'Ally. Merchant.', NULL, 'Preston Stone', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '1ea5aae7-d6c0-4589-afe1-c190743ebdbf'),
(495, 1, 2, 3, 77, '01077', 'Throwing Axe', 1, '<i>Ironborn</i> character only.\n<b>Reaction:</b> After you win a challenge in which attached character is participating as an attacker, sacrifice Throwing Axe to choose and kill a defending character.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Weapon.', NULL, 'Justin Adams', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'c3eeb001-e6a1-48ae-b310-cbd0d2c84653'),
(496, 1, 5, 3, 78, '01078', 'Great Kraken', 3, 'While you control Balon Greyjoy, he gains <abbr>stealth</abbr>.\n<b>Reaction:</b> After you win an unopposed challenge, either: draw 1 card, or gain 1 power for your faction. (Limit twice per round.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Warship.', NULL, 'Jacob Murray', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '014da37c-9903-418d-a043-ee2191b9d169'),
(497, 1, 4, 3, 81, '01081', 'Risen from the Sea', 0, '<b>Interrupt:</b> When a [greyjoy] character would be killed, save it. Then, attach Risen from the Sea to that character as a <i>Condition</i> attachment with the text: "<abbr>Terminal</abbr>. Attached character gets +1 STR."', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tommy Arnold', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0e42b4fb-8a0e-40d1-a398-fd9c0f7912a4'),
(498, 1, 4, 3, 83, '01083', 'We Do Not Sow', 1, '<b>Reaction:</b> After you win an unopposed challenge, choose an attachment or location controlled by the losing opponent, and discard it from play. (Max 1 per challenge.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tomasz Jedruszek', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '62570a84-3203-468d-9529-37dbbc6d191c'),
(499, 1, 3, 4, 84, '01084', 'Cersei Lannister', 4, 'While Cersei Lannister is attacking during an [intrigue] challenge, raise the claim value on your revealed plot card by 1.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Lady. Queen.', '"Love is poison. A sweet poison, but it will kill you all the same."', 'Tommy Arnold', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 'e5031986-0537-4892-bb7c-67a0128b5631'),
(500, 1, 3, 4, 86, '01086', 'Joffrey Baratheon', 3, '<b>Reaction:</b> After a <i>Lord</i> or <i>Lady</i> character is killed, Joffrey Baratheon gains 1 power. (Limit 3 times per round.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 3, 'Lord.', '"My son. How could I have made a son like that, Ned?" <cite>Robert Baratheon</cite>', 'Magali Villeneuve', 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'df79718d-b01d-4338-8907-7b6abff58303'),
(501, 1, 3, 4, 87, '01087', 'Ser Jaime Lannister', 6, 'Ser Jaime Lannister does not kneel when declared as an attacker in a [military] challenge, and gains <abbr>renown</abbr> while participating in a [military] challenge.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 5, 'Knight. Lord.', '"There are no men like me. There''s only me."', 'Michael Komarck', 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, 'a8854084-67e5-4955-89db-3d9cb1337789'),
(502, 1, 3, 4, 88, '01088', 'The Tickler', 2, '<b>Dominance Action:</b> Kneel The Tickler to discard the top card of an opponent''s deck. Then, you may choose 1 copy of that card, and discard it from play.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, 'Ally.', '"Tickler makes them howl so hard they piss themselves." <cite>Chiswyck</cite>', 'David Demaret', 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, '5e826f43-d1d0-4c3c-8939-789ce55bcf1d'),
(503, 1, 3, 4, 89, '01089', 'Tyrion Lannister', 5, '<abbr>Stealth</abbr>.\n<b>Reaction:</b> After an [intrigue] challenge is initiated, gain 2 gold. (Limit twice per round.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Lord.', '"When you tear out a man''s tongue, you are not proving him a liar, you''re only telling the world that you fear what he might say."', 'Jacob Murray', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, '102c0746-2205-425a-ab85-90dc41a031e3'),
(504, 1, 3, 4, 90, '01090', 'Tywin Lannister', 7, '<abbr>Renown</abbr>.\nTywin Lannister gets +1 STR for each gold in your gold pool.\n+2 Income.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 6, 'Lord.', NULL, 'Tommy Arnold', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '390a8cf7-8bc4-45c1-bea5-e6a694e9f2d5'),
(505, 1, 3, 4, 91, '01091', 'Burned Men', 2, '<abbr>Ambush</abbr> (2).', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, 'Clansman.', 'Every clan in the Mountains of the Moon feared the Burned Men, who mortified their flesh with fire to prove their courage.', 'Marc Scheff', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '30769686-a69f-4088-8939-7b9a4c4f7f76'),
(506, 1, 3, 4, 92, '01092', 'Gold Cloaks', 4, '<abbr>Ambush</abbr> (2).\n<b>Forced Interrupt:</b> When a phase ends in which Gold Cloaks entered play using <abbr>ambush</abbr>, discard it from play (cannot be saved).', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 3, 'Ally. Army.', NULL, 'David Demaret', 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, '8e70f54a-9c37-4645-9e7e-2b60a72bdb80'),
(507, 1, 3, 4, 95, '01095', 'The Queen''s Assassin', 2, '<abbr>Ambush</abbr> (4).\n<b>Reaction:</b> After The Queen''s Assassin enters play using <abbr>ambush</abbr>, choose an opponent. If you have more cards in hand than that player, he or she must choose and kill a character he or she controls.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, 'Spy.', NULL, 'Mike Capprotti', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, '1e240486-c214-4fae-aa9b-690a08a8c9aa'),
(508, 1, 2, 4, 96, '01096', 'Widow''s Wail', 1, '<abbr>Ambush</abbr> (1).\nAttached character gets +2 STR.\nIf attached character is Joffrey Baratheon, he gains a [military] icon.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Valyrian Steel. Weapon.', NULL, 'Joshua Cairós', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '4dd074aa-af6c-4897-b7b2-bff3493bcf9e'),
(509, 1, 5, 4, 97, '01097', 'Casterly Rock', 2, 'You may initiate an additional [intrigue] challenge during the challenges phase.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Stronghold. The Westerlands.', '"They say there is naught but stone at the heart of Casterly Rock." <cite>Catelyn Stark</cite>', 'Sergey Glushakov', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2267fe81-fd34-49e6-bcf5-5aa2733ac298'),
(510, 1, 5, 4, 98, '01098', 'Lannisport', 3, '<b>Reaction:</b> After you win an [intrigue] challenge, draw 1 card.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'The Westerlands.', NULL, 'Juan Carlos Barquet', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '5702d5f9-ae1e-435b-ae86-01c14817431a'),
(511, 1, 4, 4, 100, '01100', 'Hear Me Roar!', 1, '<b>Action:</b> Put a [lannister] character into play from your hand. At the end of the phase, if that card is still in play, discard it from play (cannot be saved).', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cris Griffin', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2ad9b318-4ff7-4ace-91ee-81e223fd176c'),
(512, 1, 4, 4, 101, '01101', 'The Things I Do For Love', NULL, 'Play only if you control a [lannister] <i>Lord</i> or <i>Lady</i> character.\n<b>Challenges Action:</b> Kneel your faction card to choose a character with printed cost X or lower controlled by an opponent, and return it to its owner''s hand.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Aaron Riley', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '6d93075c-8517-44ef-8580-f4fdfe1967da'),
(513, 1, 3, 5, 104, '01104', 'Arianne Martell', 5, '<b>Action:</b> Put a character with printed cost 5 or lower into play from your hand. Then, return Arianne Martell to your hand (cannot be saved). (Limit once per phase.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Lady.', NULL, 'Tiziano Baracchi', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'fa34ed25-de84-45c9-89c1-1428ec505458'),
(514, 1, 3, 5, 105, '01105', 'Doran Martell', 6, '<abbr>Insight</abbr>.\nEach other [martell] <i>Lord</i> and <i>Lady</i> character you control gets +1 STR for each plot card in your used pile.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Lord.', '"Who fears to walk upon the grass? But it is the grass that hides the viper from his enemies and shelters him until he strikes."', 'Tawny Fritzinger', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, '295184b5-9b32-45d7-a870-c2a5580e1f75'),
(515, 1, 3, 5, 111, '01111', 'Dornish Paramour', 3, '<b>Reaction:</b> After Dornish Paramour is declared as an attacker, choose a character controlled by the defending player. That character must be declared as a defender for this challenge, if able.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 3, 'Companion.', NULL, 'Sedone Thongvilay', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'f70034a0-01a1-4e77-8dde-44c1cd7d3f40'),
(516, 1, 2, 5, 115, '01115', 'Dawn', 2, 'Attached character gets +1 STR for each plot card in your used pile.\nWhile attached character has the <i>House Dayne</i> trait, it gains <abbr>intimidate</abbr>.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Weapon.', NULL, 'Henning Ludvigsen', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '9e6bf142-159b-4a3b-9d4c-d8bf233a6f0c'),
(517, 1, 4, 5, 120, '01120', 'Unbowed, Unbent, Unbroken', 0, 'Play only if you are not the first player.\n<b>Reaction:</b> After you lose a challenge as the defending player, name a challenge type. Until the end of the phase, the winner of the challenge cannot initiate challenges of that type. (Max 1 per challenge.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Daniel Rudnicki', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'ad97966b-2d52-4b03-a8f4-f51c8a63a8c9'),
(518, 1, 3, 6, 122, '01122', 'Benjen Stark', 5, 'Each <i>Ranger</i> character you control cannot be bypassed by <abbr>stealth</abbr>.\n<b>Interrupt:</b> When Benjen Stark is killed, gain 2 power for your faction. Then, shuffle him back into your deck instead of placing him in your dead pile.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Ranger.', NULL, 'Tiziano Baracchi', 1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 'dcbbfe54-078f-44c9-88e7-02efe235911c'),
(519, 1, 3, 6, 123, '01123', 'Ghost', 4, 'No attachments. <abbr>Stealth</abbr>.\n<b>Reaction:</b> After Ghost bypasses a character using <abbr>stealth</abbr>, that character cannot be declared as a defender for any challenges until the end of the phase.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 3, 'Direwolf.', '"He''s not like the others. He never makes a sound. That''s why I named him Ghost.”\n <cite>Jon Snow</cite>', 'Jacob Murray', 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, '9c0f0dce-2809-4ad9-bc27-ba5bb15484ee'),
(520, 1, 3, 6, 124, '01124', 'Jon Snow', 6, 'No attachments except <i>Weapon</i>.\nWhile Jon Snow is standing, he is considered to be participating in each challenge in which you control another attacking [nightswatch] character.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 'Bastard. Steward.', '"Different roads sometimes lead to the same castle."', 'Michael Komarck', 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'a773532a-9c2b-4b33-9052-ed73ce2d6e18'),
(521, 1, 3, 6, 125, '01125', 'Maester Aemon', 3, 'No attachments.\n<b>Interrupt:</b> When a [nightswatch] character would be killed, kneel Master Aemon to save it.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, 'Maester. Steward.', '"Kill the boy, Jon Snow. Winter is almost upon us. Kill the boy and let the man be born."', 'Leonardo Borazio', 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, '157ee453-9a78-480a-bf0e-93d74c49dc88'),
(522, 1, 3, 6, 126, '01126', 'Old Bear Mormont', 7, 'While you control The Wall, Old Bear Mormont does not kneel when declared as a defender.\n<b>Interrupt:</b> When the challenges phase ends, if you have not lost a challenge as the defending player this phase, put a [nightswatch] card into play from your hand.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 6, 'Commander. Lord.', '"The things we love destroy us every time, lad. Remember that."', 'Antonio José Manzanedo', 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 'fd60e197-476c-4d8d-811f-e0a403a12b48'),
(523, 1, 3, 6, 127, '01127', 'Samwell Tarly', 2, '<abbr>Insight</abbr>.\n+1 Reserve.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 1, 'Steward.', 'The world was full of cravens who pretended to be heroes; it took a queer sort of courage to admit to cowardice as Samwell Tarly had.', 'Thomas Denmark', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 'aab739f7-aae2-4228-a446-89c4e7f91ea2'),
(524, 1, 3, 6, 129, '01129', 'Yoren', 3, '<b>Reaction:</b> After you marshal Yoren, choose a character with printed cost 3 or lower in an opponent''s discard pile, and put it into play under your control.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, 'Wandering Crow.', '"I got thirty this time, men and boys all bound for the Wall…"', 'Dleoblack', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, '47f94d62-7d83-4e36-80c6-0062d56aa820'),
(525, 1, 3, 6, 130, '01130', 'Messenger Raven', 1, 'No attachments.\n<b>Dominance Action:</b> Return Messenger Raven to your hand to draw 1 card.', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 1, 'Raven.', NULL, 'Zezhou Chen', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '0ebedb0f-d94c-4f8f-a478-2cffc712c6c7'),
(526, 1, 3, 6, 131, '01131', 'Old Forest Hunter', 2, 'No attachments except <i>Weapon</i>.\n<b>Action:</b> Discard 1 card from your hand to gain 1 gold. (Limit once per phase.)', '2015-07-09 10:43:54', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 1, 'Ranger.', NULL, 'Taylor Ingvarsson', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '89207067-9a33-4689-9b8a-66c85f7c68c1'),
