(601, 1, 2, 1, 32, '01032', 'Seal of the Hand', 3, '<i>Lord</i> or <i>Lady</i> character only.\n<b>Action:</b> Kneel Seal of the Hand to stand attached character.', '2015-08-10 08:43:30', '2015-08-24 13:57:08', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'Item.', 'The king eats, they say, and the Hand takes the shit." <cite>Robert Baratheon</cite>', 'Mauro Dal Bo', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'f97ccf1a-5b0d-490f-9968-78330e92171c'),
